Package: enrichdot
Type: Package
Title: Publication-Ready Enrichment Dotplots with Automatic Layout
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: person("Jianhua", "Zhu", email = "XiaoLi1991-star@users.noreply.github.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Author: Jianhua Zhu [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Jianhua Zhu <XiaoLi1991-star@users.noreply.github.com>
Description: Lightweight ggplot2 helpers for polished enrichment dotplots from
    already prepared enrichment result tables. Long terms are wrapped, dot and
    text sizes are chosen automatically, and fixed-panel saving keeps the
    plotting area stable. Resolved automatic parameters are printed to support
    agent-assisted tuning without re-running enrichment analysis.
